column5: What a great year! Team 7 "THE ROD BENDERS" smash last years totals for the win. Also beating last years totals was Team 1 "RIPPIN' WEEDS" in a very close battle to the end.  A big thanks to the captains and participants for making this interesting and fun to the very end!
Wow, close race for 1st and 2nd.  Congrat's team 7!
maybe next year each team tosses some money to a pot and the proceeds can be dontated to the winners charity of choice
We did it!!! who hoo First year in this for me and we win!! I think that next year there should be a $1 entry fee that goes towards t-shirts or hats for the winning team!! Go Team 7...
The job is available, send Roy a PM if you want it.
Awesome Tourney!  A huge thanks to Slowpoke for running this!   Great work Rod Benders!
Thanks SlowPoke, you did an awesome job.  We would never think of taking it away from you.  And a big thanks to GBW for being our captain.
A job well done Slowpoke And a round of for Fisherpete,our team captain!
